data.description: Welcome to this exquisite coastal retreat by David Weekley in the sought-after Enclave at Town Center. Upgraded home boasts an open design w/wood plank flooring thruout the main living areas. The chef's kitchen is a culinary delight boasting a massive center island/bar ideal for entertaining + comes fully equipped with stainless appliances. The split bedroom arrangement offers privacy w/the primary bedroom showcasing a vaulted ceiling, arched window & luxurious ensuite bath.  The bath is a spa-like oasis w/a huge walk-in shower while the walk-in closet provides loads of storage. Convenience is key in the separate laundry room equipped with a full sized washer & dryer. Step outside to the pavered screened lanai offering a perfect spot to unwind & enjoy the private views. 2 car attached garage provides secure parking. Tankless hot water heater & newer water softener. Located on one of the best lots in Enclave. Enjoy the award winning Nocatee amenities, take a short golf cart ride to shops and restaurants or drive to the pristine beaches just a few miles away. Easy walk to the water park since the path is directly across the street.  Don't miss this opportunity to make this coastal haven your dream home!
